Workhorse MBT of the US Military for almost half a century, the MACE variant introduces cutting-edge targeting systems for the latest smart munitions. Armed with a stabilized smoothbore 120mm main gun and powered by a 1,500hp gas turbine engine, the 70-ton M1 can identify and destroy enemy targets out to 5km while traveling at a blistering 45mph. The MACE also adds an advanced APS capable of jamming and intercepting most anti-armor munitions, including ATGMs. “Whispering Death” is still in its prime.

The LATV4 Recon is an open-chassis all-terrain vehicle originally designed for US Special Operations search and rescue missions. Armed with a top-mounted MMG and packing a powerful 450hp engine with a max speed of 100mph, the LATV4 is ideal for lightning squad assaults and extractions. Although a lack of armor can leave it vulnerable to enemy fire, the reduced weight increases maneuverability and allows it to be air-dropped into the combat zone. Mount up the squad and rollout! Just don't stand still.

The Impávido was escorting the Exodus to shelter out of Wolff’s reach. Blasco told Zain this was it, no more. She wanted nothing to do with Oz and his No-Pat agenda. 

She spoke with Bergman, the Nordvik Executive, before leaving. He’d provided the CIA with false information about Exodus’s heading, sending them on a wild goose chase. Once they realized what he’d done, they’d retaliate. 

“I’m a dead man already. May as well do some good.”

It stuck with her.

BRANI ISLAND, SINGAPORE.

For years, rising sea levels and increased storm patterns suggested dire consequences for the shipping industry on Brani Island. Rather than accepting this fate, the Singaporean government chose to tackle the problem and initiated the massive SeaWall project. The port thrives today and is heavily relied upon as a key part of America’s supply network.

Russia targets the port as a key strategic location and launches an offensive, but America moves quickly to repel enemy forces and protect their interests in the region.

He was assigned command of the Exodus, a refugee rescue vessel and deployment ship. Onboard, lived an elite task force that would undertake covert operations to further the No-Pat cause. Irish knew then Oz needed to be stopped. He won’t rest until that happens.

Irish joined the Marine Corps and proved himself a highly capable soldier across a series of international deployments. He was earmarked for a specialist unit called Tombstone Squad and overcame his long standing alcohol addiction to earn his place. The squad was one of the fiercest units in the US military and was called upon for only the toughest missions. One of their last ops involved a Chinese coup and a nearly averted world war that left Irish embittered by the loss of his compatriots.

Timely delivery of Health and Ammo crates are an essential part of sustaining battlefield operations. After an engagement your teammates will inevitably be low on ammunition, and probably health. A well-placed crate can replenishment both, allowing friendly forces to regroup and push on to the next objective. Prioritize support crates within your squad so everyone can stay in the fight, and keep an eye out for other friendlies in need of a few bullets and bandages.

US Special Operations scout helicopter in service since 1960, the modern variant MD540 Nightbird is designed for quick insertion/extraction and air support missions. Pylons can be fitted with M134 miniguns, M260 FFAR rocket pods, AGM-114 hellfire missiles, or GAU-19 .50 gatling guns. Highly maneuverable and traveling at speeds of up to 90 knots, a skilled 2-man crew can execute daring rooftop landings and low-level “Gun Runs”. Outboard personnel benches allow for a squad to hitch a ride to or from any hot LZ. The Nightbird rewards the most creative aviators.

**%{PYRITE_SUBROUTINE}** blocks are special blocks that are similar to **%{PYRITE_RULE}** blocks, but do not have a designated **%{PYRITE_EVENT}**. A **%{PYRITE_SUBROUTINE}** block's **%{PYRITE_ACTIONS}** will be executed when called from the **%{PYRITE_RULE}** block. Like **%{PYRITE_RULE}** blocks, **%{PYRITE_SUBROUTINE}** blocks can have a **%{PYRITE_CONDITION}** to determine whether or not the **%{PYRITE_ACTIONS}** inside should execute.
  
  An important note is payload values, including %{ID_ARRIVAL_BLOCK_EVENTPLAYER}, %{ID_ARRIVAL_BLOCK_EVENTOTHERPLAYER}, and %{ID_ARRIVAL_BLOCK_EVENTTEAM}, use the context of the **%{PYRITE_RULE}** block in which the **%{PYRITE_SUBROUTINE}** instance block is placed in. An example of this would be, if your **%{PYRITE_RULE}** block has an instance of %{ID_ARRIVAL_BLOCK_EVENTPLAYER}, and the **%{PYRITE_SUBROUTINE}** is called in %{ID_ARRIVAL_MODBUILDER_EVENT_ONPLAYERDEPLOYED}, it would use the %{ID_ARRIVAL_BLOCK_EVENTPLAYER} associated with %{ID_ARRIVAL_MODBUILDER_EVENT_ONPLAYERDEPLOYED}. Be careful with this, as you will run into errors if your **%{PYRITE_SUBROUTINE}** is placed inside a **%{PYRITE_RULE}** block with non-existant payloads for that **%{PYRITE_EVENT}**.

He underwent intensive rehabilitation and began adapting to life with prosthetic legs. Undeterred, he returned to New Cairo City and volunteered at a No-Pat shelter. It was here that he met Oz who saw in the young man someone who had overcome extreme hardship with his spirit intact.

“Hey, newbie.”

Her shoulders tightened. When was the last time she’d heard her name, rather than ‘greenhorn’, ‘newbie’, ‘recruit’?

“Yeah?”

“Message for you. Private line.”

The radio sat alone in a shadowed cargo container. Static popped before a cold, authoritative voice left the speaker. One she knew.

“Did you make your decision?”

Her gun was already loaded. “Yeah. I’m in.”

“Good. Execute the rest of your unit and the Dark Market will pay handsomely.”

Without hesitation, her finger slipped toward the trigger.

US Special Operations scout helicopter in service since 1960, the modern variant MD540 Nightbird is designed for quick insertion/extraction and air support missions. Highly maneuverable and traveling at speeds up to 90 knots, a skilled 2-man crew can execute daring rooftop landings and low-level “Gun Runs”. Outboard personnel benches allow for a squad to hitch a ride to or from any hot LZ. The Nightbird rewards the most creative aviators.

Driven, autonomous and capable, Ji-Soo Paik specializes in intelligence gathering and infiltration. Born in Gwangjiu, South Korea, she rose to be an Olympic level speed skater before military conscription intervened. Paik enjoyed a successful career in ROK-SOF, earning herself the moniker “Gumiho” – named after the Korean mythological shapeshifting fox. The official story claims a failed mission ended her career in disgrace, after which she joined the No-Pats. But who believes official stories anymore?

The EBLC-Ram charged along the mountain pass, leaving the battle of Black Ridge in its wake. Inside the vehicle, Wolff sat stone-faced. It was undeniable: Operation Steadfast Refuge was compromised.

Oz was behind this attack. Most likely with Dark Market help. They’d come for Shearwater tech and succeeded. Was Oz planning another Blackout? Or something worse?

Regardless, the tech was useless without an engineer to operate it. Better yet, the creator. Dr. Voros. It was imperative they found him first.
Hey Boris, time to do your thing, baby. Make it fast!

Once upon a time, Charlie Crawford was MI6. He was supposed to protect His Majesty’s realm, not screw it over by selling weapons to foreign powers. But weapons were his speciality. It’s why the Dark Market recruited him.

It’s also why they sprung him from custody. He still had so much to offer. But he needed to be put on ice for a while. Ironic, Crawford thought, Panama felt more like a fucking furnace.

Angel ran as helicopter gunfire thumped the ground and chased him behind a boulder. The chopper zoomed overhead - it was already turning. Exposed, with nowhere to run, Angel gripped his rifle. The missile rocketed past him - fire and smoke gushing from its rear as it climbed up into the sky and collided with the aircraft in a mighty explosion. Angel looked round as the soldier lowered the smoking rocket launcher from her shoulder. He hadn’t seen Lis in years. This reunion was shaping up to be special.

US premiere stealth fighter developed for air superiority and first strike missions. The F35E upgrade combines CTOL/STOVL/CV variants for streamlined production while introducing enhanced countermeasures for stealth-defeating radar. Its design prioritizes a low radar signature coupled with long-range targeting, allowing the Panther to penetrate deep into enemy air space and neutralize air/ground threats while remaining largely undetected. Capable of vertical hover and speeds up to Mach 1.6, the F35 is factory armed with a 25mm GAU rotary cannon and a combined inboard/outboard munitions payload of 8,160kg.
